# -- $0: GLOSSARY --
# Sigil   | Name         | Expansion | Risk | Description
# --------+--------------+-----------+------+----------------------------------------------
# IDN     | identity     | attrs     | B    | Actor identity
# FCS     | focus        | attrs     | H    | Current attention anchor
# OBJ     | objective    | attrs     | B    | Active mission
# WRK     | work         | attrs     | B    | Current operational state
# STP     | step         | contenido | M    | Next immediate action
# SES     | session      | attrs     | B    | Recent compressed episode
# LNG     | lesson       | contenido | M    | Learned operational rule
# KNW     | knowledge    | attrs     | B    | Stable project knowledge
# REF     | reference    | attrs     | B    | Audit reference
# CNST    | constraint   | attrs     | M    | Active operational limit
# AUD     | audit        | contenido | M    | Validation or release audit record
# TAG     | tag          | attrs     | B    | Classification metadata

